Text: i guess everyone quit watching chelsea?  it just gets a little frustrating when a kajillion versions of the same crappy show get uploaded five seconds after airing and it takes like a week to get this, especially considering all these green and pink skull users work as a team.  just imagine how long it would take if they were actually individual users?  it'd be YEARS!  anyway, hopefully you get around to it while the show is still on television.
